{"descriptions":[{"id":1360,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་འདྲས་\u003c/span\u003e is associated with nouns and adjectives:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདེང་སང་ཁྱེད་རང་སྐུ་གཟུགས་ག་འདྲས་འདུག\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How\u0026rsquo;s your health these days?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་ལོ་དཀར་ཆུ་ག་འདྲས་འདུག\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How\u0026rsquo;s the dairy production this year?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལྟོས་དང་། ཁོང་མགྱོགས་པོ་ག་འདྲས་འགྲོ་གི་འདུག\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Look! How quickly he\u0026rsquo;s walking!\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་འདྲས་ཟེ་\u003c/span\u003e is associated with verbs. This adverbial form makes it possible to ask about the way in which an action is performed:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་འདྲས་ཟེ་རྒྱག་དགོས་རེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How should it be done?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཁོང་བོད་ནས་ག་འདྲས་ཟེ་ཕེབས་པ་རེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;How did he come from Tibet?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe literary form of \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་འདྲས་\u003c/span\u003e is \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་འདྲ་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe suffix \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཟེ་\u003c/span\u003e of the words \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་འདྲས་ཟེ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་ག་ཟེ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའདི་འདྲས་ཟེ་\u003c/span\u003e is sometimes also spelled \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསེ་\u003c/span\u003e: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་འདྲས་སེ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eད་ག་སེ་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའདི་འདྲས་སེ་\u003c/span\u003e. The first spelling is preferred for etymological reasons: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཟེ་\u003c/span\u003e is in fact derived from the verb \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཟེར་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;to say.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:43 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:43 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}